  {
    "start": 119.0,
    "end": 127.56,
    "text": "Avoid practicing too fast in a tense or erratic way."
  },
  {
    "start": 127.56,
    "end": 132.24,
    "text": "Stay focused on control and speed will come naturally."
  },
  {
    "start": 132.24,
    "end": 140.56,
    "text": "Second, having found your target fastest relaxed controlled speed, play at a steady tempo at"
  },
  {
    "start": 140.56,
